**** Installation ****
Download the archive or clone it.

Copy the file to /usr/bin
$ sudo cp /path/to/siv /usr/bin/

Give permissions
$ sudo chmod 755 /usr/bin/siv

**** Help ****
Usage: /path/to/siv [argument]
List of arguments,
	-g >\tGentoo Linux Theme
	-s >\tStar Wars Theme
	-v >\tDarth Vader Theme
	-t >\tStar Trek Theme
	-h >\tShow Help

Example: /path/to/siv -g
